    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors against the project requirements for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven show achieved levels below required levels. Six factors remain not-assessed and constitute identified epistemic gaps. Despite the narrative references to project requirements throughout this assessment, the structured bindsRequirement linkage is absent from this package record. The overall credibility package is structurally submitted for review under the Minimal profile.",
